replies.body:
I agree. While old WW would be definitely neutral evil, new WW is definitely chaotic good. He's obviously doing what he thinks is right with a good, selfless intention and doesn't give a damn about laws or codes. I'd probably say he's the best example of chaotic good we have right now. For reference, here are the chart of the champions I personally think best represent each type, it makes it easier put him on the CG slot when you compare him with an obvious chaotic neutral like Jinx (who just does what she wants without a care for laws nor if it's good or evil), or any of the evil ones.

